description: The foodies of DC go to this blazing red truck for some amazingly tasty Peruvian fusion cuisine. El Fuego’s menu includes traditional dishes like...Ceviche- zesty and refreshing marinated tilapia and shrimp, hot pepper, cilantro and spices, served on a bed of fresh lettuce with crunchy corn chipsEl Choripan- scrumptious grilled sausage on a toasted roll with delicious guacamoleSignature Lomo Saltado Bowl- authentic stir-fry with tender beef tenderloin, red onions, plum tomatoes, and hot peppers...to name a few. Whether you come visit El Fuego on the streets or invite the truck to come cater your next event, if your appetite is on fire, let this fiercely flavorful food fan the flame.
name: El Fuego
